@{
    Layout = "_Layout1";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQs</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-icons/1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        p,h6
         {
             margin-left:15px
         }
         .text-primary
         {
          color:#1c63a7;
         }
         .bg-custom
         {
            background-color:#1c63a7;

         }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="py-5 bg-light">
        <h3 class="text-center mb-4 pb-2 text-primary fw-bold">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
        <p class="text-center mb-5">
            Have questions? Find answers to the most common inquiries about our services below.
        </p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-concierge-bell text-primary pe-2"></i> What types of services do you offer?
                </h6>
                <p>
                    We provide a wide range of services, including home maintenance, technical support, IT solutions, and lifestyle assistance. Check our Services section for full details.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock text-primary pe-2"></i> How quickly can I book a service?
                </h6>
                <p>
                    You can book a service instantly through our website or app. Our team will confirm your request and schedule the service at your earliest convenience.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-users text-primary pe-2"></i> Are your service providers qualified?
                </h6>
                <p>
                    Absolutely! All our service providers are thoroughly vetted, trained, and experienced professionals dedicated to delivering quality services.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-wallet text-primary pe-2"></i> What are the payment options?
                </h6>
                <p>
                    We accept multiple payment methods, including credit/debit cards, online payments, and bank transfers. All transactions are securely processed.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-primary pe-2"></i> Is there a guarantee for your services?
                </h6>
                <p>
                    Yes, we stand behind the quality of our services. If you're not satisfied, we’ll work with you to make it right.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <h6 class="mb-3 text-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-calendar-check text-primary pe-2"></i> Can I reschedule or cancel a booking?
                </h6>
                <p>
                    Of course! You can easily reschedule or cancel your booking through your account. Please refer to our cancellation policy for details.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>